  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/Night%27s_Watch\" title=\"Night&#39;s Watch\"><img alt=\"Night&#39;s Watch.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/f/f3/Night%27s_Watch.svg/50px-Night%27s_Watch.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/f/f3/Night%27s_Watch.svg/75px-Night%27s_Watch.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/f/f3/Night%27s_Watch.svg/100px-Night%27s_Watch.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\">Arron</td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/Night%27s_Watch\" title=\"Night&#39;s Watch\"><img alt=\"Night&#39;s Watch.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/f/f3/Night%27s_Watch.svg/50px-Night%27s_Watch.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/f/f3/Night%27s_Watch.svg/75px-Night%27s_Watch.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/f/f3/Night%27s_Watch.svg/100px-Night%27s_Watch.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"infobox-image\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<a href=\"/index.php/File:Arron_and_Emrick_(ACoK_Comic).jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Arron and Emrick (ACoK Comic).jpg\" src=\"/images/6/6f/Arron_and_Emrick_%28ACoK_Comic%29.jpg\" width=\"239\" height=\"374\" /></a><div>Arron and Emrick by Mel Rubi for <a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings_(comics)\" title=\"A Clash of Kings (comics)\"><i>A Clash of Kings</i> comic</a></div></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<hr /></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiance</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Night%27s_Watch\" title=\"Night&#39;s Watch\">Night's Watch</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Westermen\" title=\"Westermen\">Westermen</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Born</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Fair_Isle\" title=\"Fair Isle\">Fair Isle</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd35.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd35.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Books</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings\" title=\"A Clash of Kings\">A Clash of Kings</a></i> (appears)</li><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords\" title=\"A Storm of Swords\">A Storm of Swords</a></i> (appears)</li><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows\" title=\"A Feast for Crows\">A Feast for Crows</a></i> (appendix)</li><li><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i> (appears)</li></ul></div></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Arron</b> is a <a href=\"/index.php/Night%27s_Watch\" title=\"Night&#39;s Watch\">Night's Watch</a> recruit. He is the twin brother of <a href=\"/index.php/Emrick\" title=\"Emrick\">Emrick</a>, and is from <a href=\"/index.php/Fair_Isle\" title=\"Fair Isle\">Fair Isle</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffcappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffcappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd35.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd35.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Appearance_and_Character\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Appearance and Character</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Recent_Events\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Recent Events</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#A_Clash_of_Kings\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Clash of Kings</i></span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#A_Storm_of_Swords\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Storm of Swords</i></span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#A_Dance_with_Dragons\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.3</span> <span class=\"toctext\"><i>A Dance with Dragons</i></span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Appearance_and_Character\">Appearance and Character</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Arron&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Appearance and Character\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Like his twin brother, Arron is blond. They are orphans.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok6.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok6.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recent_Events\">Recent Events</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Arron&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Recent Events\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Clash_of_Kings\"><i>A Clash of Kings</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Arron&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Clash of Kings\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>Emrick arrives at the <a href=\"/index.php/Wall\" title=\"Wall\">Wall</a> with the <a href=\"/index.php/Wandering_crow\" title=\"Wandering crow\">wandering crow</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Conwy\" title=\"Conwy\">Conwy</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok6.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok6.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Storm_of_Swords\"><i>A Storm of Swords</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Arron&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Storm of Swords\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>Arron is trained in the martial arts by <a href=\"/index.php/Jon_Snow\" title=\"Jon Snow\">Jon Snow</a> due to the loss of Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Endrew_Tarth\" title=\"Endrew Tarth\">Endrew Tarth</a>, the master-at-arms at <a href=\"/index.php/Castle_Black\" title=\"Castle Black\">Castle Black</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos75.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos75.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Dance_with_Dragons\"><i>A Dance with Dragons</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Arron&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Dance with Dragons\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>Arron and his brother Emrick swear their vows with four other recruits (<a href=\"/index.php/Hareth_(Mole%27s_Town)\" title=\"Hareth (Mole&#39;s Town)\">Horse</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Satin\" title=\"Satin\">Satin</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Leathers\" title=\"Leathers\">Leathers</a>, and <a href=\"/index.php/Jax\" title=\"Jax\">Jax</a>) at the grove of <a href=\"/index.php/Weirwood\" title=\"Weirwood\">weirwoods</a> north of <a href=\"/index.php/Castle_Black\" title=\"Castle Black\">Castle Black</a>, inside the <a href=\"/index.php/Haunted_forest\" title=\"Haunted forest\">haunted forest</a>. They are escorted by Jon, now <a href=\"/index.php/Lord_Commander_of_the_Night%27s_Watch\" title=\"Lord Commander of the Night&#39;s Watch\">Lord Commander</a>, along with ten rangers. Jon, <a href=\"/index.php/Emmett\" title=\"Emmett\">Iron Emmett</a>, and <a href=\"/index.php/Bowen_Marsh\" title=\"Bowen Marsh\">Bowen Marsh</a> weigh each recruit and assign them to an order. Arron is assigned to the <a href=\"/index.php/Stewards\" title=\"Stewards\">stewards</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd35.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd35.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Arron&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Radwd35.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd35.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd35.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\">1.1</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd35.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\">1.2</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons-Chapter_35\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons-Chapter 35\">Chapter 35</a>, Jon VII.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Raffcappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raffcappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows\" title=\"A Feast for Crows\">A Feast for Crows</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows-Appendix\" title=\"A Feast for Crows-Appendix\">Appendix</a>.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Racok6.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Racok6.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\">3.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Racok6.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-1\">3.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings\" title=\"A Clash of Kings\">A Clash of Kings</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Clash_of_Kings-Chapter_6\" title=\"A Clash of Kings-Chapter 6\">Chapter 6</a>, Jon I.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rasos75.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rasos75.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords\" title=\"A Storm of Swords\">A Storm of Swords</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_75\" title=\"A Storm of Swords-Chapter 75\">Chapter 75</a>, Samwell IV.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached tim